Question:
====================Question====================
If two expressions are $24 - 8$ and $12 + 4$, will they form equation
Solution_text:
====================Solution====================
To check equality of expressions we will check if both of them give same result or not
First expression $24 - 8 = 16$
Second expression $12 + 4 = 16$
Since both expression give same values i.e. $16$, answer is True
